org.iotivity.service

Class RcsValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.iotivity.service.RcsValue

  • public final class RcsValue
extends java.lang.Object
    Value holds a value among various types at a time. Type helps identify type information of Value.
    See Also:
    RcsResourceAttributes, RcsValue.Type
